{"tid":1198292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔好覺得自己一個好大影響力","createTime":"2019-06-10T07:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:04:15.000Z","uid":176699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c8ec8a668f722baaebc1a1c2df38d068c00eef","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"但同時都唔好覺得團結嘅力量好渺小<br />\n<br />\n一人一步，路由人走出來<br />\n<br />\n琴日一百萬人上街絕非易事<br />\n<br />\n只要做自己認為做得岩嘅事就夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算你支持衝擊也好，定和理非也好<br />\n<br />\n我地到最後都係同一個目標努力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做警察嘅，問下自己所做嘅係咪過到自己良心，對得住你家人嘅未來<br />\n<br />\n出嚟行嘅，做你認為岩嘅事就夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n612再見"},{"pid":"a6ccc01f0deb6eeb5a15319e7c048c8c955ae579","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"我地得一個目標"},{"pid":"6e8517fc24dc0209b32fde9b51d710c19ed0343b","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"就係守護我地嘅香港，守護我地與身俱來嘅權利"},{"pid":"7fc2580123d0d0313b5d7ffa1af89d4648d3d4c2","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:48:04.000Z","msg":"多你一個好多<br />\n<br />\n叫埋身邊嘅人一齊，好多時佢地都係覺得無力感好重，所以不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我地可以話俾佢地知係有彎轉<br />\n<br />\n可以拎返我地嘅野"},{"pid":"34074cb46ee11842083f60d085be78726001e568","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"387f5c85e3737086d81e1bed5e16f5f33bcd2df6","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:50:58.000Z","msg":"無論你係邊個<br />\n<br />\n只要你有心想香港好<br />\n<br />\n就算做鍵士，都有你嘅作用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但行多一步，就係你呢一步，可能足以我地扭轉局面"},{"pid":"a28a1c1c457735bce628ceb6d183a838f6f359fe","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"連登有個笑話<br />\n<br />\n個答案係<br />\n<br />\n蟻多嬲死象<br />\n<br />\n螻蟻尚且偷生，何況是人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚟呀，俾次機會自己"},{"pid":"cc22c386d3e4021581a879946ec0a566a4aa17bd","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"就算死，都要死得轟烈"},{"pid":"f2ea604151224298e0fa5d20df6104b5de5e403a","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"定你甘於被蠶食？"},{"pid":"cd42fe734385c85136436a0fe1a75e8e8f325d85","tid":1198292,"uid":182777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxtmnHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxtmnHh.png&h=027bdc62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d09cc2fd08e75d8770030424777fad1e78bcc953","tid":1198292,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}